{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_01","textHome":"我住在这个住宅区，我的朋友也都住在附近。@我基本上都和清佳还有未都在一起。@过去或是现在，我们都在公园里玩耍聊天……@还有，我喜欢制作零食，也会拜托她们试吃！@嘛，虽然基本上都是未都一个人吃光……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_18","textHome":"现在，在此刻一起度过这段时光，@是多么偶然的一件事。@所以，我想和我有着关系的人们，@都是无法替代的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_19","textHome":"嗯……这样子我就能说出来了吧……@我，状态超好！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_20","textHome":"怎么回事……@心中的朦胧一下子被驱散了的感觉！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_21","textHome":"做点心虽然有很多窍门，@但是最重要的还是材料的用量！@母亲是这样告诉我的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_22","textHome":"没有收集好材料就开始做点心，@一心想着用别的材料来代替，@结果却总是失败……虽然创新很有趣，@但是忠于配方才理所当然是制作的基础……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_23","textHome":"跟点心的完成最有关系的我想还是手法。@和面的方法有着很多的诀窍。@我在这方面还远远不够啊……@所以只好依靠修行才行呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_24","textHome":"啊！这里这里！很感谢你能来！@那么……今天也拜托你了！@总感觉有些害羞呢，唔呼呼！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_25","textHome":"早上好！昨天睡得好吗？@啊，肚子叫了，被听到了吗？@啊哈哈……一醒过来肚子就饿了……@那么，去吃早饭吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_26","textHome":"你喜欢食堂的什么菜呢？@我很喜欢食堂有时会有的布丁和果冻！@食堂提供的甜点，会有特别的感觉呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_27","textHome":"这个时间，有回家的孩子们，@还有买完东西回来的人，工作结束回来的人。@小区里一下子变得热闹起来了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.3,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_03","textHome":"不管前方有什么在等待着我，@我……都必须要努力才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_28","textHome":"小区里，虽然有热闹的时候，@但晚上望向外面的时候，也能感受到寂静。@我十分喜欢这样的感觉。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":1}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_29","textHome":"看着小区，想着这寥寥可数的大楼中，@充斥着各种各样的生活，@就会有种不可思议的心情呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_30","textHome":"我所走的道路，也是魔法少女的道路……@是不可以从那里逃离的对吧……@那么，就只好前进了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_31","textHome":"这就是完全未知的领域吧……@要比平常更加小心行动才行，@不然一定会遭到算计！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_32","textHome":"呜哇～有这么多的人……我，没问题吗……@不行不行！我要振作一点！@好，就看看我能做到何种程度吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_33","textHome":"你知道玛德莲蛋糕吗？@听说是用第一个制作它的人的名字来命名的。@这样的点心还有很多吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_34","textHome":"我啊，喜欢大型建筑物的……那种氛围。@反过来，我也喜欢从大型建筑物里@向远处眺望的感觉。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_35","textHome":"我不太受得了黑巧克力，@所以我一直都选择牛奶巧克力。@等长大了也许我的口味就会变了吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_36","textHome":"小时候会从楼梯上往下跑，经常惹大人生气。@现在已经不会这么做了！@除非是……上学快迟到的时候……啊哈哈……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_37","textHome":"我最喜欢我住的住宅区了！@到了春天，周围的樱花都开放的时候，@真是好美啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_04","textHome":"一定会有办法的……然后……@不对……要想个办法才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_38","textHome":"因为我最喜欢生奶油了，@所以自己做的时候，总是忍不住去偷吃！@但总是会被妈妈发现……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":300}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_39","textHome":"我们的住宅区，夏天会开祭典哦！@大家一起来装饰，一起摆摊……@还有盂兰盆舞哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.2,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_40","textHome":"我喜欢自己做奶油泡芙吃了！@中间是淡奶油和奶黄的双重奶油最棒了！@外面的脆皮我也很喜欢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":301300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3013_00_41","textHome":"我不只喜欢甜点……我还喜欢各种零食！@鱿鱼干、鲑鱼干、干贝！还有，牛肉干！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301300,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,